Skip Homeier is always one of those what'shisname kinda actors. A face and a
cool, punk composure always familiar and hard to forget. A lot of guest roles in numerous series including WANTED DEAD OR ALIVE, PERRY MASON...and
I'm just taking wild guesses here. It's a treat to see him in almost the main role in this one.
